      "created_at": "2024-04-21T10:39:38.237Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hmm, this is very interesting. I have looked at stuff like this Smartspin.  I might have even talked to that guy at some point.  I have smart trainers but I also have a spin bike which I really like so this has been interesting to me.  Even though this is a bad business decision <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> meaning you are a very niche user, for some reason I really like this so if you would be willing to work with my developer we could try to figure out how to fix this.  I would like to better understand this problem.  If so just let me know and I will give you info on how we can connect.  It should not take a huge amount of your time.</p>",
