      "cooked": "<p>That I don\u2019t know. I\u2019m going to do a test today or tomorrow and send them the logs to see if the can see where the disconnect is happening. I did see on GitHub where they did a recent fix where they were having issue with TD and erratic ERG but that issue was fixed and closed I believe.</p>\n<p>Anthony and Emad are super responsive so I\u2019m hoping we can get a fix on one side or the other. Thank you!</p>",
