      "created_at": "2024-04-22T18:57:40.603Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I did a ride today and had the same issue. ERG dropped out about two minutes in and ERG button became disabled for the rest of the ride. I have submitted an issue to SS2K github also. Just did a couple of short test rides for testing and the second one quit controlling the trainer on the second interval but this time the ERG button did not go off. I can send the logs to you also but not sure if that would help your developers. Thanks!</p>",
