      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/c4cdca/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2024-04-28T15:51:55.719Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex! This should be fixed on our end. The breaking feature stemmed from sending ERG set points every second. I haven\u2019t seen any other apps that do that. Typically they\u2019re (watt targets or set points) only sent when there\u2019s a new target.</p>\n<p>Regardless, that should not cause an issue and so it\u2019s been fixed <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/tada.png?v=9\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\"></p>\n<p>If you\u2019d like to trade some services, perhaps we could work something out for a TrainerDay dev account so we can add you to the list of apps we routinely test and endorse.</p>\n<p>Have an awesome weekend!</p>",
