      "created_at": "2025-05-03T03:16:45.190Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi All,</p>\n<p>I am also experiencing similar issues with TD-SSK2 on a Schwinn 800 IC. Either SS2k continues going down in resistance, despite riding under target watts, OR at some time in the ride they seem to lose connection altogether.</p>\n<p>Wondering if there is any more recent news on this thread? Or anything I can do?  I love the simplicity of Trainer Day, be great to be able to use it with SS2k.</p>\n<p>Many thanks,</p>",
